I've read most of the reviews & was hesitant in placing my order with them. I placed the order with them anyway because I love Afghan food & my experience was great!
The person who delivered my food was a gentlemen name Shafi who was very nice & courteous. Their Afghan food is good, not the best out there but it's better then the most. Their fried chicken & burgers are great! I've since placed my order with them 5 more times & Shafi has always delivered my food hot & fresh.
I dont know who were the other delivery guys that made people write negative reviews. If you want to place an order for delivery, I suggest you call the store & request Shafi for delivery because he truly is a nice guy.
Hope this helps future customers with their delivery orders. Afiet Olsun!
